channel.title: Need some help
channel.description:
Hey everyone I'm gonna start my own server and I need some help on questions I need answers.
Can somebody provide me with a link on these forums that has these options in a source download w/ cache's client? [I have nobody to help me so I need simple things to start out]
1. Dungeoneering 2. Summoning 3. Non Spawn 4. Slayer rewards 5. Castle Wars 6. Staff Zone 7. Donor Zone
Would anybody be interested in working on a project with me?
